BAIL HEARING - 
Defendant in custody and appearing by video from the Manitowoc County Jail.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of strangulation and suffocation.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 08-08-22 at 1:30 pm.  Bail is set at $2,000.00 recognizance bond with the conditions that he report to the Manitowoc County Sheriff's Department for fingerprints, photographs and identifying information within 48 hours or, if incarcerated, within 72 hours of release, defendant is to have no contact with D.T.W., DOB: 12-27-04 or any residence occupied by that individual, defendant must maintain absolute sobriety.   Court will allow a one-time contact with the residence, with the aid of law enforcement after the 72-hour no contact provision has expired, to obtain personal belongings.   Bail furnished and defendant is released from custody.
